Package net.socialchange.doctype

Interface Summary
Doctype Stores all information in a DOCTYPE declaration.
DoctypeGenerator Generates a new doctype declaration.
 

Class Summary
DoctypeChangerStream This class adds, removes or otherwise modifies a DOCTYPE declaration to an incoming XML document.
DoctypeImpl Read-only object representing a doctype declaration.
DoctypeParser Class for parsing a Doctype declaration and storing read information for later retrieval.
Version This class defines the version number of this code.
